        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780800792909" href="/book/show/1283289.Christy">review of another edition</a>


          <div>
    <span class="greyText">Recommended to Carly by: </span>
      <a href="/user/show/5675076-vicki-b">Vicki B</a>
  </div>


          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5662037-carly?shelf=thanks-mom">thanks-mom</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5662037-carly?shelf=christian">christian</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5662037-carly?shelf=romance">romance</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5662037-carly?shelf=historical">historical</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5662037-carly?shelf=have-re-read">have-re-read</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5662037-carly?shelf=fiction">fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5662037-carly?shelf=for-my-kids-to-read">for-my-kids-to-read</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5662037-carly?shelf=listened">listened</a>, 
