        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3402795875" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11052085747571690432">I read this for the first time when I was a teenager and was swept away then. I still find it just as mesmerizing. I love that we get to experience this new culture right along with Christy. I will say the relationship is rushed and I would have liked more development there. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


