          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780808566472" href="/book/show/3388291-christy">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/51943097-victoria-lynn?shelf=historical-fiction">historical-fiction</a>
          </div>
